{"履修期": "秋学期", "主な教授言語": "英語", "授業目的": "The main purpose of this course is to improve and develop students' communication and confidence to use English in personal, professional, and academic contexts. Although the course will focus primarily on spoken communication, lessons will also aim at developing listening, reading, and writing skills to achieve and reinforce communicative goals. Lesson goals and tasks will be centered around a wide variety of skills topics relevant to student interests. Students will be encouraged to develop their intercultural awareness by critically thinking about and expressing their ideas from personal, global, and cultural perspectives. In-class communication and other activities will aim at improving students' capacity to work collaboratively and in cooperation with classmates.&nbsp;Students will be asked to reflect on their difficulties regarding English communication, describe how they plan to overcome these difficulties, and reflect on their progress by the end of the semester.", "到達目標": "Students will improve and build their confidence to use English communicatively in a variety of situations and contexts. Students will improve their spoken English fluency: improving speaking, listening, reading, and writing needed for effective communication in a variety of situations. Students will improve their lexical range by learning and using vocabulary skills related to course content. Students will improve their critical thinking skills and will improve their intercultural awareness by exploring and sharing ideas from personal, global, and cultural perspectives. Students will reflect on their personal progress throughout the course.", "特記事項": "", "関連科目": "", "授業の概要・背景": "", "授業方法": "Course will be aimed at a face to face format, but methods of studying online will also be provided. Students will be required to do in-class activities individually and collaboratively, and complete homework as required.", "トピック": {"第1回": ["<div><span dir=\"aut